{"tid":1787838,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"選管會：公開地址助居民監察","createTime":"2019-12-18T08:14:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T08:15:21.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c595bdf79929998ac96d9bf232170926d751ace1","tid":1787838,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T08:14:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191218/44BWQJCFD2YR7LNHHEHTKYRDK4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191218%2F44BWQJCFD2YR7LNHHEHTKYRDK4%2F&d=hjTGTk%2FOBCUjzD4XQyU%2Bui8lxPyN12Ak3mY6G5vlvHI%3D&h=dd086ecb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191218%2F44BWQJCFD2YR7LNHHEHTKYRDK4%2F&h=4699cbf7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191218/44BWQJCFD2YR7LNHHEHTKYRDK4/</a><br />\n<br />\n選管會：公開地址助居民監察<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/9UsgEUcdllzwaSDnOEBA_2ESavo=/802x531/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/NJU6W762RMB5SU35AVE73LDW5Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2F9UsgEUcdllzwaSDnOEBA_2ESavo%3D%2F802x531%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FNJU6W762RMB5SU35AVE73LDW5Q.jpg&h=d0dfbaa6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n資深大律師石永泰昨代表香港記者協會陳詞。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【選民登記冊私隱案】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警察隊員佐級協會不滿選管會的選民登記冊將姓名住址一同公開，侵犯私隱，令警務人員受「起底」威脅，提出司法覆核，案件續審。選管會一方昨指，部份有問題的選民登記或要靠當區擁有「當地智慧」的普通市民才可發現；容許公眾和傳媒查冊，可監察及填補當局查核機制的不足之處。法官押後裁決。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記協引《蘋果》報道證需要<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：社區放TG 「如攻擊市民」<br />\n<br />\n代表選管會的資深大律師梁偉文指，若不靠公眾或傳媒協助監察，實難以揭發全部有問題的登記資料。他舉例指，假如某個登記地址的樓層根本不存在，對涉事建築物有認知的當區居民可輕易揭發問題，但僅憑書信往來的政府職員卻未必能及時發現。<br />\n<br />\n香港記者協會早前獲准介入訴訟，昨由資深大律師石永泰代表陳詞。石指出，一個文明和健康的社會，有賴傳媒作為第四權去監察選舉。若要參與公民社會，就必須犧牲部份個人私隱。<br />\n<br />\n石又引用《蘋果日報》2011年揭報道作例子，指當年報道刊登後，確有人被警方拘捕。若選民登記冊將選民姓名和地址分開提供，兩堆資料將無法讓傳媒有效偵察。<br />\n<br />\n此外，石亦擔心若法庭接納以保護私隱為由，禁止公眾查閱選民登記冊，同樣情況亦可套用在公司及土地登記冊上，嚴重影響公眾知情權。石強調，「起底」一般在網上匿名行事，涉事者不會親身到選舉事務處查閱選民登記冊並留下個人資料。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：HCAL3042/19<br />\n■記者伍嘉豪、劉偉琪"},{"pid":"186e510e90228d9d6d8b84a0bb2e7bf1f7942d78","tid":1787838,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T08:14:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cMC8VCF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcMC8VCF.jpg&h=36102201&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0suoQ2O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0suoQ2O.jpg&h=203fa15f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NTntx6h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNTntx6h.jpg&h=228c1213&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0c5e5767255ad89aedee56ffc90c8a703f8457d5","tid":1787838,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T08:15:21.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}